<br>
I am not saying many Druids do not have the experience of casters prefering Ageo.  I am just saying, if you are in a guild that acts that way, start making posts to your guild message boards explaining the difference to them.  They will eventualy come around.  Once PotG is a raid essential tool on your guild, MGB becomes an obvious first choice for class abilities. <p>____________<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=13463"
