From complaints here, however, it looks like many druids are experiencing even casters not wanting PotG.  IMO, this is probably out of convenience more than anything else.  Clerics not coordinating well and overwriting PotG, casters not thinking to click off Ageo with PotG casting is announced, etc.  All bad habits out of which I think people should take the time to educate their Guilds.  Even if PotG is only being used for casters, MGB would still be usefull for Druids. <p>____________<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=13463"
