<br>
If MM was ever obtained, I could see the casters coming around for the extra hitpoints and not having to refresh symbol so often.   But getting that spell isnt that easy as it requires getting a 2nd floor commander key (highly camped mob for emperor key) and it is a rare drop - my guild went months without getting the key while farming Ssra and finally got 3 in 2 days ;p.  Once you get the key, then you gotta deal with all the other guilds killing the HP (can anyone say competition similar to NTOV when Vulaak was still alive??) and finally hope it drops once dead.   We've killed THO many times and still have never obtained the wizard nuke.  <p>Fayne Dethe<BR> 
