Hp/mana100 FT6 priest shields, the Sporecaller (inventory clickable druid-only 570 DoT), and various other goodies!<br>
<br>
There's usually one (very rarely two) guilds on each server, at the moment, that kill the High Priest regularly, so the MGB issue for druids is restricted to the minority at the moment.  Marzin's Mark is tradable, though - but an uncommon drop from the creature.  It's definitely an enjoyable fight whilst you're still learning it, I'd recommend heading towards that general area if you're considering your options.  ^_^<br>
